    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Which actions are you thinking should show up in the notification area? I thought about this at one point, but figured it would make the notification area too busy with messages.\n\nIt will be rather non trivial to have the menu items show the keyboard shortcut as the information is determined dynamically in a manner that can't be looked up by action, only by the keypress. It would require us to create \"names\" for each action. But even that is bound to fail as people customize things as they can make subtle changes to how actions happen. In other words, our \"actions\" are not simple atomic things, they are complete JavaScript functions that make arbitrary calls to our API. Not sure what we want to do with this.\n"
  },
